title: Tuesday Post Show (01-25-22)
itunes:title: Tuesday Post Show (01-25-22)
description:
Bobby starts by wondering why there was a pile of cash sitting in his spot this morning. Bobby lists the Top 5 things he cares about the most. Bobby talks about Meatloaf passing away and the meaning behind his most famous song. Eddie’s son won a big award at school. Bobby also runs through some news stories he hasn’t been able to get to during the radio show.
